          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-14 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-20">
            <div>
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#4f39f6]">Maps Ranking Trend Dashboard</span>
              <h3 class="mt-3 font-sans text-[1.75rem] font-semibold leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.025em] text-[#111827]">Watch your rank move as automation compounds over 90 days.</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 font-sans text-[1rem] leading-relaxed text-[#57534e]">The ranking trend view shows your local pack position for each target keyword tracked daily over the last 30, 60, or 90 days. The correlation is clear: consistent GBP activity drives position up. Skipped weeks show up as flat stretches. Stacc makes sure the trend is always moving in the right direction — because the work never stops running.</p>
              <a href="/features/rank-tracking/" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[12px] font-semibold text-[#4f39f6] hover:underline">See rank tracking <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4f39f6" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#e7e5e4] bg-white p-8 shadow-[0_8px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]">
